headline: EQT Corporation (EQT) Tops Q2 Earnings Estimates
summary: EQT (EQT) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of +2.27% and -10.81%, respectively, for the quarter ended June 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?

headline: FTC May Free VanLoh’s Quantum in Marcellus Over EQT-Tug Hill Deal
summary: Federal Trade Commission restrictions were put on Quantum Capital Group in 2023 over the $5.2 billion sale of No. 11 Marcellus producer Tug Hill and its midstream unit XcL Midstream to EQT Corp.
